In this challenge we have rsa.py

from Crypto.Util.number import getStrongPrime, bytes_to_long
f = open("flag.txt").read()
m = bytes_to_long(f.encode())
p = getStrongPrime(512)
q = getStrongPrime(512)
n = p*q
e = 65537
c = pow(m,e,n)
print("n =",n)

print("c =",c)
